    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "First acute anterior myocardial infarction in patients with primary PCI preoperative and postoperative 30 days intensive dose atorvastatin statin therapy compared with conventional -dose therapy , patients can improve left ventricular function , reduce major adverse cardiovascular events ."
    },
